Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Connecting old words\Nthat have been used up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to convey\Nmy simple thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day's faint wind blows away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the castle ruins of yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.49,0:00:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll laugh with you\Nand live for the moment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still that incident\Nwill continue to trouble you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.40,0:00:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it must be good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:01:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving nothing behind,\Nlet us share what is left
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In time, we'll realize\Nthat it was everything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.15,0:01:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And sadness will touch our cheeks,\Ncreating a river of tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trembling thoughts swept into a vortex\Nand melting away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty impressive…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.03,0:02:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You timed it well to scatter\Nthe three to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have practiced quite a bit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it is a pretty complicated song…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did you\Nimmediately understand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I’m manipulating\Nthese guys with my flute
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you understood\Nhow difficult this song is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.36,0:02:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a pretty impressive punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can’t completely\Nunderstand this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True… Since art is so foreign to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since she uses that flute\Nto manipulate,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it means that song must contain\Nindividually specific sound patterns
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to control each and every movement\Nof those guys…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m pretty confident when it comes\Nto just analyzing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this time it’s not looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t understand\Nmusical notes whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakeout: Shikamaru's Comeback!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll specially show you\Nthe Camellia Dance next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn’t say things\Nyou can’t even do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bone is harder than steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have a taste of it\Nwith your own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no one that’s heard\Nthis song and lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finale, Ninth Passage,\NDemon Revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The melody’s changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something’s gonna come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The speed at which he flees\Nafter determining
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that these Material Ghosts\Nare dangerous…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve used my precious Paper Bombs\Nand Smoke Bombs all at once
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all I could do was hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That white one…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bit off my physical energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing that shuriken passed through,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that thing is semi-materialistic\Nwith very little mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Chakra itself with an appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s probably Chakra that’s shaped\Nmostly by mental energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why it seeks stability\Nand craves for physical energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I continue dealing with\Nthose “Hungry Chakra”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t be able to build up my Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re pretty dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s a Shinobi who can\Nmake special Chakra like me…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s without a doubt, a Secret Ninjutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means I should leave\Nthe white thing alone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and aim for the main body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The quickest way would be\Nto stop the sound of the flute, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it’d be impossible to get close to\Nthat woman in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next thing would be to capture\Nthose three with Shadow Possession Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's difficult too since they’re\Nattacking me separately at different times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I let even one escape\NI’d be attacked and it’d be the end…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren’t any openings in\Neither offense or defense this woman…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh! She might be\Na pretty good Shogi player.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My remaining Ninja tools\Nare twelve kunai knives,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nine shuriken, twelve meters of wire,\None Flash Bomb and one Paper Bomb…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I’m playing without\Nrooks or bishops.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I lose them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that’s not possible…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akamaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Eat this, Akamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don’t eat you won’t\Nget your strength back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Akamaru, let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s the issue of those guys too…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance of the Camellia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no use hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you can predict\Nthese guys’ movements
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there’s nowhere you can run, little rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll find you and break you\Ninto pieces right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Everything’s ready.\NAll that remains is to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’ll be nine attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The outcome will be decided\Nduring the attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wishful thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Jutsu manipulated by\Nthis sound is invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:11:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever plans you have\Nto win against me…is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scampering around, you little rat!\NWhere are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you’re over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it’s a cheap trick.\NYou think you can make a fool of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five…six…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,seven…eight…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scurrying around to get away.\NWhat is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s lengthened the shadows\Nwith light and …
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Possession Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Possession Jutsu…\Na success!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s impossible…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How were you able to predict\Nthese guys’ movements?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way you could have heard\Nthe differences in my music patterns!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn’t listening to\Nthe sounds at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s something other\Nthan the sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that give away your command patterns,\Nisn’t there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The movement of the three...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you memorized\Nmy finger movements and predicted?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way that’s possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your right index finger\Nand ring finger…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound that you make\Nwith those
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,along with the left middle finger\Nand pinkie,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that middle crab pincher man\Nstands ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your right thumb and index finger,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:14:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and your left index finger and pinkie,\Nthe club man charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you were dodging my attacks\Nand looking for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was observing each and every one\Nof your finger moves in detail…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,analyzing and memorizing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s no use…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re bound by\NShadow Possession Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most interesting rule\Nof the Shogi play is that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can use pieces you obtain\Nas your own pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on out…\Nit’s my turn to attack…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I’ll hunt you down\Nusing the three pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re looking pretty composed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand ready with a kunai knife\Nat least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My weapon is just this flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that there hasn’t been a person
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who’s heard the sound of\Nthis flute and lived, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s some confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad you aren’t able to\Nuse the pieces, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next it’s my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Possession Jutsu,\Nsuccessful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I’d hunt you down\Nusing the pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used the three pieces as bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In attacking, the first hand\Nis the trick, a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The basics are to score\Nwith the second hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it’s come to this\NI’ll need to force out with power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t think that I’d get to\Nsecond state in a place like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It ticks me off but…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll acknowledge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy was a pretty impressive scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is…this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true you’re somewhat sharp, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won’t go as\Nyou’ve planned from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:17:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she gonna force herself out\Nof the Shadow Possession Jutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s with that tremendous Chakra?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Jutsu’s gonna come loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t be worrying about\Nsaving Chakra anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no other way\Nbut to use that Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Art: Shadow Strangle Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he grabbing my body\Nwith the shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s just as if I’m being grabbed\Nby a real hand…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, no more than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! What an incredible strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this distance\NI’ll lose to that strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Flute: Chains of Fantasia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a…Genjutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you aiming?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t move my body…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While in second stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I manipulate many Genjutsu\Nwith my flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of those, this one is\Nan appropriate for that little rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason is…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:19:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Genjutsu stops the movement\Nof the prey and ties it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How’s that? How’s it feel to\Nbe the one tied up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this was your last move huh?\NUnfortunately, it’s a return checkmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He broke his own finger\Nwith his own shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he release the Genjutsu\Nwith that pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, he kept pretending to\Nbe bound by the Jutsu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you this already
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the first hand is the trick,\Na fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The basics are to score\Nwith the second move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover this second move…\Nit’s a little different from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the Shadow Strangle Jutsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the closer in distance you are\Nto the subject the stronger the hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. I carelessly got too close…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that’s not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most careless thing was\Nthe words you said earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“my weapon is just the flute.”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re looking pretty composed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand ready with a kunai knife at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My weapon is just this flute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that\Nthere hasn’t been a person
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who’s heard the sound of this flute\Nand lived, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I threw the kunai knife\Nright in front of you and missed…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was to lead you to pick it up\Nand come closer to me, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you think it was\Na bother if I approached you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite my doubts,\NI worked up my courage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My clumsy attempts with words
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.69,0:21:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You listened without turning away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.07,0:22:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder I get carried away by you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don’t feel anything for me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.95,0:22:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so sad
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.11,0:22:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.45,0:22:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.70,0:22:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you smiled
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I was able to speak
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my own words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.24,0:22:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time, I spoke to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, that’s ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.86,0:22:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I having a dream or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.45,0:22:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it’s too intense to be a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:23:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That suit with its outstanding\Nventilation and supple fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.95,0:23:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, those eyes,\Nthat hair, those eyebrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Why are you here…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: “The Leaf’s Handsome Devil!”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.40,0:23:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense the approach of a storm!
